@base = http://localhost:5000

### Health
GET {{base}}/health

### Modes
GET {{base}}/modes

### Words
GET {{base}}/words?language=java&difficulty=easy&count=15

### Save score (team)
POST {{base}}/scores
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user-001",
  "displayName": "Taro",
  "teamId": "team-a",
  "scope": "team",
  "language": "java",
  "difficulty": "easy",
  "correctChars": 220,
  "wpm": 65,
  "accuracy": 96.5,
  "missCount": 3
}

### Team ranking
GET {{base}}/rankings?scope=team&language=java&difficulty=easy&teamId=team-a&top=10
